title: Louisiana Lockdown - Season 1
description:
Louisiana Lockdown - Season 1

On Louisiana Lockdown, Warden Cain and his staff are faced with many obstacles from, running a rodeo, to a natural disaster, and raising their families who live on the prison grounds, all while managing some of the most dangerous inmates in the country. Will the reward for good behavior be enough for the prisoners to turn their lives around?

Ep 1 - Killer Roadtrip
Ep 2 - Prison Suicide
Ep 3 - Drug Bust
Ep 4 - Hunger Strike
Ep 5 - Bones
Ep 6 - Escape
Ep 7 - Death Ride
Ep 8 - After Midnight
